text: Ocean's 11 is a 1960 American crime comedy heist movie directed by Lewis Milestone and starring Frank Sinatra, Dean Martin, Sammy Davis Jr., Peter Lawford, Joey Bishop, Angie Dickinson, Cesar Romero, Richard Conte, Henry Silva, Buddy Lester.
